Commands
All commands shown

"/" is the original prefix of the script in which all bots will respond to.
[Argument] an argument is what you should put after a command e.g. /float >5<
in this case I added a "5".
Descriptions are common sense.
🔐 Authorization Commands 🔐
**/**`adduser `[player] - Authorize player to use commands *(Main account only)*
**/**`removeuser `[player] - Remove user's command access *(Main account only)*
🎮 Fun Commands 🎮
